Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.08,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,940)\fscy66\fscx66\blur4}Simpanan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:46.80,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Jika ada sesuatu yang terjadi, dan\Norang-orang kampung ini dalam bahaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.64,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,sebagai teman-sejati,\Nsaya pasti akan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.69,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, jaga diri ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.69,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.23,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas segalanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.44,Sara,Sara,0,0,0,,Kami juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.65,Orfia,Orfia,0,0,0,,Semoga selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.78,Alma,Alma,0,0,0,,Jaga diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:05.95,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Latifa... Tolong tengokkan adik saya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.87,Sara,Sara,0,0,0,,Serahkan sahaja pada kami!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.29,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Jumpa lagi ya, Onii-chan! {\fscy89\fscx65}TwT
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.88,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baiklah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.05,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Selamat jalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.18,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, selamat jalan!
